data.description: Tri-Palm Estates 55+ new on market. 4 bed 2 bath home on Fee Land with a 433a certification on permanant foundation which is required for FHA financing. This home has many upgrades, remodeled, in a great area, centrally located near restaurants, shopping and more. Enjoy the Tri Palm country club setting with golf course and clubhouse in development, schedule your showing today!
